'From Squeak 2.1 of June 30, 1998 on 8 September 1998 at 9:45:42 pm'!"Change Set:		IRCMiscDate:			8 September 1998Author:			Lex Spoonchanges IRC makes to the system, outside of NetTools-IRC"!!Character methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ls 9/5/1998 01:18'!asIRCLowercase	"convert to lowercase, using IRC's rules"	self == $[ ifTrue: [ ^ ${ ].	self == $] ifTrue: [ ^ $} ].	self == $\ ifTrue: [ ^ $| ].	^self asLowercase! !!NetNameResolver class methodsFor: 'lookups' stamp: 'ls 9/5/1998 01:14'!addressForName: aString	^self addressForName: aString timeout: 60! !!String methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ls 9/5/1998 01:19'!asIRCLowercase	"Answer a String made up from the receiver whose characters are all 	lowercase, where 'lowercase' is by IRC's definition"	^self collect: [ :c | c asIRCLowercase ]! !